Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:04.420
Miwok ilovasini ochganimizda biz birinchi 
bo‘lib kategoriyalar ro‘yxatini korishimiz mumkin.

00:00:04.420 --> 00:00:08.390
Endi, bu yerda biz bir necha kategoriyalarni 
ko‘rishimiz mumkin, va bu ro‘yxat ancha aniq.

00:00:08.390 --> 00:00:09.330
Xo‘sh, bu holatda,

00:00:09.330 --> 00:00:13.670
biz vertikal linear layout ishlatgan holda
 4 ta TextView ni tirab qoyishimiz mumkin. 

00:00:13.670 --> 00:00:16.670
Ammo numbers activity ga kirganimizdan so‘ng, 

00:00:16.670 --> 00:00:19.230
mana shu elementlar ro‘yxati yanada murakkabroq ko‘rinishga ega bo‘lishi mumkinligini ko‘ramiz.

00:00:19.230 --> 00:00:22.500
Biz bu ro‘yxatga ancha lug‘at
 so‘zlarini qo‘shsak bo‘lar edi.

00:00:22.500 --> 00:00:26.120
Masalan, 1 dan 1000 gacha bo‘lgan 
raqamlarni yozishga qaror qilib.

00:00:26.120 --> 00:00:30.480
Bu ro‘yxat esa viewer davriyligi uchun yaxshi ishlatsa bo‘ladigan holat.

00:00:30.480 --> 00:00:32.940
Hozir esa men sizlarga bizning kodni qanday 
qilib list view hamda adapter massivni 

00:00:32.940 --> 00:00:35.630
ishlatish uchun o‘zgartirish 
kerakligini ko‘rsataman. 

00:00:35.630 --> 00:00:38.680
Bilaman, hozir juda ko‘p tushunchalar bo‘lib
 ketyapti, lekin havotirga o‘rin yo‘q.

00:00:38.680 --> 00:00:40.670
Biz bitta-bitta qadam tashlaymiz.

00:00:40.670 --> 00:00:44.380
Birinchi navbatda, men sizning telefoningizda ishlaydigan kodni olib uni ishga tushirishingizni xohlardim.

00:00:44.380 --> 00:00:47.356
So‘ng, biroz bularning hammasi 
qanday birga ishlashini kuzatuv

00:00:47.356 --> 00:00:48.241
qilishingizni istardim.

00:00:48.241 --> 00:00:49.200
Undan keyin,

00:00:49.200 --> 00:00:52.490
biz sahna ortida nima bo‘layotganiga 
nazar tashlaymiz.

